name: FBBB Cruiser XL 27" Red with Yellow wheels.
description:
At 27" long and 7.5" wide the PLUS is a slightly bigger version of the original FBBB Cruiser is to suit shredders with larger feet or if you prefer a more standard skateboard feel this is for you.

They still have the plastic injection molded deck, Which provides just the right amount of flex and makes them extremely durable. 
So say goodbye to de-lams and soggy decks, Ride these all year round!

The trucks are 3.5" still making them really easy to turn, This combined with the ABEC7 Bearings makes for a super fun smooth and fast ride.

Get places faster on an FBBB Cruiser..

See instagram #fbbbcruisers for more pics.

UK Shipping Only 

Thanks.
